# Mobile Screenshot Placeholder

This is a placeholder for the mobile application screenshot.

To add the mobile screenshot:
1. Take a screenshot of your running application on mobile device or mobile emulator
2. Save it as `screenshot-mobile.png` in the project root
3. The README.md will automatically display it

The mobile screenshot should show:
- Single-column layout
- Bottom navigation bar
- Message list optimized for mobile
- Touch-friendly interface elements
- Responsive design adaptations
